OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779152633
OL,3,CMSPs to elect new first minister after
OL,4,CScottish elections
OL,6,FMSPs will vote for Scotland's newest
OL,7,Ffirst minister following the Holyrood
OL,8,Felections.
OL,10,FJohn Swinney, the serving First
OL,11,FMinister, said he is confident he will
OL,12,Fwin the vote.
OL,14,FHowever, all five other parties at
OL,15,FHolyrood have said they will also put
OL,16,Ftheir leaders up for the top job.
OL,18,FThe SNP won 58 seats at the Scottish
OL,19,FParliament elections, making it by far
OL,20,Fthe largest party but short of the 65
OL,21,Fseats needed for a majority.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779152633
OL,3,CMSPs to elect new first minister after
OL,4,CScottish elections
OL,6,FMr Swinney will need the help of at
OL,7,Fleast one other party, which in
OL,8,Fprevious years has come from the
OL,9,FGreens.
OL,11,FAhead of Tuesday's vote, the party has
OL,12,Fcalled on Mr Swinney to honour his
OL,13,Fpromise to introduce a vote on a
OL,14,Fsecond referendum on the first sitting
OL,15,Fof his new government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779152633
OL,3,CMSPs to elect new first minister after
OL,4,CScottish elections
OL,6,FMr Swinney promised during the
OL,7,Fcampaign that a new SNP administration
OL,8,Fwould bring forward a vote to approve
OL,9,Fthe development of a Section 30 order,
OL,10,Fwhich would be needed to transfer
OL,11,Fpowers to hold a referendum from
OL,12,FWestminster to Holyrood.
OL,14,FSince the powers are reserved, the
OL,15,Fvote would act as a message to express
OL,16,Fthe will of the Scottish Parliament
OL,17,Fand pressure the UK Government to
OL,18,Fapprove a second vote on the union.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
