PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779152634
OL,3,CMSPs to elect new first minister after
OL,4,CScottish elections
OL,6,FGillian Mackay, co-leader of the
OL,7,FScottish Greens who will stand for the
OL,8,Ffirst minister vote, said Scotland had
OL,9,Fvoted for a pro-independence majority
OL,10,FParliament, "and that must be
OL,11,Frespected".
OL,13,FShe added: "If John Swinney is elected
OL,14,Ffirst minister on Tuesday, then his
OL,15,Fnew government must bring forward the
OL,16,Fpromised parliamentary debate and vote
OL,17,Fon Scotland's right to choose at the
OL,18,Ffirst available opportunity."
OL,26,@rD@MOUsD@JO]uD@LOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
