CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779152634
OL,3,CMSPs to elect new first minister after
OL,4,CScottish elections
OL,6,FThe election of the first minister
OL,7,Fwill take place on Tuesday afternoon,
OL,8,Fwith the winning candidate likely to
OL,9,Fbe sworn in at the Court of Session on
OL,10,FWednesday and appoint a cabinet that
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,13,FThursday will be taken up by the vote
OL,14,Fto confirm the appointment of
OL,15,Fministers, with the inaugural First
OL,16,FMinister's Questions of the
OL,17,Fparliamentary term due to take place
OL,18,Fnext week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
